column3:
Eshana's next task is not for the squeamish.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
Survey the designated location and defeat any slugs that appear.
You are truly a sssight for sore eyes, my friend.
Our ssscouts recently had the misfortune of spotting a monstrous slug near Dimwold. Their grotesque appearance and corrosive slime─it is enough to make one ssspew.

They mussst be dealt with, but I am ashamed to confess the Gatekeepers are ill-sssuited to fight them. The mere sight of them is enough to make mossst convulse. And those who manage to approach are then irreparably scarred by their acidic ssslavering.
Please, I beg of you─go to Dimwold and rid us of this blight on the land.
Is it done, then? Is the ssslug no more?
You have my humblessst thanks. If the Gatekeepers should encounter another, you can be certain we will call for you again.
